      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hilton%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "Originally called Unionville, the village incorporated in 1885 as North Parma before becoming Hilton.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
